description: A Chromium-based WPF/WinForms component that can be embedded into your .NET application to display modern web pages built with HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, Silverlight etc.
releaseNotes:
DotNetBrowser 1.3 contains the following features and improvements:

    Support of Windows 10 and .NET 4.6 has been implemented.
    Cookies API has been added.
    Custom Context Menu has been added.
    File Downloads API has been implemented.
summary: Solution for integration of Chromium-based component into .NET applications.
title: DotNetBrowser
